            </div>
        </center>
        <center>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>Lunches</h2>
                <ul>
                    Make sure to keep up with the latest updates from your childrens school
                </ul>
                <a class="btn btn-default" href="Messages">
                    Messages
                </a>
            </div>
        </center>
</div>
